text: Schöndorf is a municipality in the Trier-Saarburg district, in Rhineland- Palatinate, Germany. As of 31 December 2018, 773 people lived there. == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Municipalities in Rhineland-Palatinate Category:Trier-Saarburg
